Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:10.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:15.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:17.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:22.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:25.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:31.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:35.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:43.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:48.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:53.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:59.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:04.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:11.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:16.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:21.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:27.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:32.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:10.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:15.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:17.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:22.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:25.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:31.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:35.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:43.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:48.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:53.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:59.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:04.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:11.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:14.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:21.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:27.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:32.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:41.48,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}{\pos(146,358)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}00之声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想做什么 能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要洋装
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃更多的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去太空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意够帅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太强了根本不用打了嘛 大将
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是变革者的作风 真过瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭?首都圈全域?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 苏伊尔国王和参加会谈的同志们也被卷了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛哈尔支部长…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦用了核武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是从空中用大功率激光攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento Mori…建立了超乎预想的功勋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能轻松扫清反政府势力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 真正意义上消除世界上的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(365,367)}拉格朗日3  资源卫星群
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00-Raiser TRANS-AM到达极限时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我能感觉到上校的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越理论极限值的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会这样 Twin Drive远远超乎我们的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 00-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 我看过你的身体数据了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今怎能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 保守一点尽力而为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 观测系统捕捉到地球圈内有异常热源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请速来舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…卫星武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是应用了太阳能发电的武器 虽然掌握的情报很少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中东 苏伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:04:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 利冯兹·阿尔马克的做法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维修完毕后 托勒密立即出航
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始联邦卫星兵器破坏任务 全员各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 在此之前 我有些事要和大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在背后操纵联邦 企图支配世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过他们 他们的名称是…变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用太阳能发电的卫星激光攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这攻击范围…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的宇宙部队已展开破坏卫星武器的行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队兵分两路同时攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗舰23艘 MS43架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是宇宙部队的全部战力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 卫星武器周边有A-LAWS舰队坐守
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这战力还不知能不能行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田 天人有联络吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只有靠KATARON单干了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda孕育出的生体终端 变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他们操纵A-LAWS 还掌握了Veda吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 是从我们开始武力介入的5年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就开始活动了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trinity 让3架Gundam Throne加入武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将30架搭载拟GN炉的GN-X提供给联合国 也是他们干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说他们改变了伊欧利亚的计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此洛克昂和克莉丝他们才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何把这么重要的事隐瞒至今
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说要继续实行伊欧利亚·舒恩伯格的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若这是事实 可能我们才是异端
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 创立A-LAWS 虐杀反政府势力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种做法不可能换来真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒A-LAWS 驱逐变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要遵循自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我一个 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我也和他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情大概明白了 不过 现在必须做的是破坏敌人的卫星兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·诺列嘉
